{"tid":436155,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【卡努襲港】往機場塞爆棄車 青衣區公路現拖篋人潮","createTime":"2017-10-15T02:25:30.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-15T03:01:24.000Z","uid":84436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"df282586d2548e66b45d597201141449ead02914","tid":436155,"uid":84436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T02:25:30.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/breaking/20171015/57333921\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fbreaking%2F20171015%2F57333921&d=lIJcOy1SdpiccVNprGOqLeI2ZYfPb188nwqbwuz8hpE%3D&h=0b885f44\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fbreaking%2F20171015%2F57333921&h=9e7dab0f\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/breaking/20171015/57333921</a><br />\n<br />\n颱風卡努襲港，天文台於早上8時40分改發8號東北烈風或暴風訊號。受到風暴影響，青馬大橋、汀九橋、昂船洲大橋及青嶼幹線都有封路等強風管制措施，所有車輛需改行青馬大橋下層出入機場及禁止使用馬灣路出入馬灣，同時長青隧道去機場需要間封，導致青馬管制區一帶入機場的交通今早嚴重擠塞，往機場的巴士排出一字長龍。<br />\n<br />\n運輸署表示，由於車多關係，青嶼幹線來回方向、長青公路往機場方向、長青隧道往機場方向、青衣北岸公路往機場方向，及北大嶼山公路往九龍方向，交通擠塞。"},{"pid":"5787132a2d20362e2a793c3ebf6cb4437c807de3","tid":436155,"uid":48124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T03:01:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}